get_synonyms()¶

united_geonames.models.update_centroid(sender, instance, **kwargs)¶

On saving each UnitedGeoNameSynonym object this method gets all UnitedGeoNameSynonym objects in current UnitedGeoName and calculate centroid of each UnitedGeoNameSynonyms. Then writes centroid to table UnitedGeoName (column “centroid”).
